{"tid":1506443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想多謝琴日發夢幫過我嘅手足","createTime":"2019-08-25T19:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T21:26:26.000Z","uid":145611,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e38413c02db65003a0625305167063fb9578daf","tid":1506443,"uid":145611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:58:47.000Z","msg":"琴日傍晚發夢嘅時候，我係其中一批喺荃新天地附近俾警察截停搜身搜袋既人，嗰陣比20幾個警察圍住。<br />\n我淨係記得警察好多支鏡頭影住我自己，要我清楚講出自己嘅名同埋身分證號碼，應該係要交上去做紀錄（雖然唔係第一次俾人查身分證）。<br />\n搜完之後，當下好迷惘唔知點做，冇意識要帶返面罩。嗰陣有位巴打主動走埋嚟，舉起把遮擋住好多人嘅視線同我講咗一句：唔使驚慢慢來，帶返好個面罩先。<br />\n好多謝你呢一句簡單嘅說話，為我打左一支強心針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你有緣睇到呢個po既，想講一聲多謝你，希望你琴日相安無事，之後繼續努力。<br />\n其實一句支持說話已經係對身邊嘅人好大鼓勵，最後香港人加油！"},{"pid":"5faddd8da5e8ddb06cb30c2e406181550507ad3e","tid":1506443,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670bb40caefdb080850e61133212eacde2ce551e","tid":1506443,"uid":74591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:09:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5835a824a8190a3b237e80f059b00ccd69cdb99","tid":1506443,"uid":161025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:13:51.000Z","msg":"推 多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d3f2a262ce01b29e0a47b337a6490e90ddc27b","tid":1506443,"uid":169020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:18:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"391c440bd81d684b0155da21e3b812312c900d8e","tid":1506443,"uid":65210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:26:26.000Z","msg":"［開飯/住宿/義診/搵工］你班前線死廢青 未成年中學雞同我入黎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503091</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}